text: Carlos Garcia (born 11 September 1942) is a Cuban gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1942 births Category:Living people Category:Cuban male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Cuba Category:Gymnasts at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Pan American Games medalists in gymnastics Category:Pan American Games silver medalists for Cuba Category:Gymnasts at the 1967 Pan American Games
